
1  

Yakob ebulesit loka Edeke ka loka Ejakait Yesu Kristo, Mama ejaas atekerin atomon kanuarei nuesiarakinos:

Yoga.


2  

Iinacanaka, koomitos kere araut nukaiyalama, naidoioto toma acodunio nakiponesio luipu, 
3  

kojenete ebe aitemio naka aiyuunikus eyauni atitiŋikin, 
4  Ido kojau atitiŋikin kaswam naedoliorit, tetere iraunos luipolok, luitekoro, komam adiokirot nakiwolikinit.


5  

Arai ejai kayes yenewolikinit acoa, kilip Edeke loeinakini kere kajalit, kwabo mam itoroni, ŋes da einakinio. 
6  

Konye kilip kotoma aiyuun, komam ebuonokin, naarai yenebuonokini eputosi bala akailan naka aŋolol, naekutanari ekwam kibukanari. 
7  Kinyek ituŋanan ŋin aomit ebe edumuni ibore kama ejai Ejakait; 
8  ituŋanan yenika itauon iarei, yenimam icasit korotinike kere.


9  

Konye koolobob onace loitisilitoi kanuka aitopoloorioke, 
10  

koolobob lokabaran da kanuka aitisilioke, naarai eraraar kwape aturot naka inya. 
11  Naarai elomuni akoloŋ isirinyori amwanis inya, edoi aturotoke, eoliori da ajokis naka aputoke. Isokokoi lokabaran da kwape kwaŋin kotoma alositeke.


12  

Isirereŋitoi etuŋanan loetitiŋikin acodunio, naarai kedau acamunio, edumuni aboko naka aijar naisumunikinit Ejakait lueminasi ŋes. 
13  Kinyek yenecodunio einer ebe, “Edeke kacoduni eoŋ” naarai mam epedori Edeke acodunio kanukaronok, ido ŋes elopet mam ecoduni ituŋanan kere. 
14  

Konye ŋinituŋanan ecodunio kiriite ekeimiel elopet kaijodijodio, 
15  Kosodi kepotuu eimiel euriei adiakar, adiakar ŋin da kepoloor idouni atwanare.


16  Ikainacan luminan, siriŋalas. 
17  

Ŋiniinakinet naejok, ka ŋiniijaikina naedolit ebuni kokuju, ijesuni kama ejai Papa loka luecaete, emamei ailoconokin kamakeŋ, karaida etoribe loka aibelonokin. 
18  

Kanuka akoteke abu kouri oni kakirot naka abeit, tetere kirauni kwape araito nusodit nuka isubanake.


19  

Ijenete ŋin, iinacanaka luminan. Aso korai ŋinituŋanan yenisunyit aiirar, yeniyapi einer, yeniyapi anyunyura, 
20  

naarai anyunyura naka etuŋanan mam iswamai adolit naka Edeke. 
21  

Kanuka ŋun kolacasi asilianut kere ka aronis naelitoro, kijaut kaiyapepera akirot nairaitai toma, naepedori aitajar aijarakus.


22  

Konye koraas ikeswamak akirot, kwabo mere ikeirarak bon, luimodas. 
23  Naarai arai iirari ituŋanan akirot, komam iswamai, eputosi ŋin ituŋanan yeneanyuni akonyen nuka aurioke kotoma aroet; 
24  naarai eanyuni, kolot, atipet imurwokini kwape eputor. 
25  

Konye yenirerei ikisila luedolito, luka aosikinio, kodunyakinite kotomakec, sirikeraun ikeiraran yenimurwokini, konye ikeswaman aswam, isirereŋitoi ituŋanan ŋin kotoma kanuiswamai.


26  

Arai eomit ituŋanan kere ebe erai yenikedini, komam itikokin aŋajepeke, kiŋalai etauke, edini loka ituŋanan kaŋin erai lotai. 
27  Edini loelai, loemamei elos kakonyen nuka Edeke Papa ŋes lota: aanyanar ikokiok ka apuserun kotoma ocanikec, ka aidar bon kakwap komamei amasikinet.

